title: Waterproof Dog Leash, Long Training Lead for Dogs 5 m / 10 m / 15 m / 30 m Odor Resistant Suitable for Small, Medium and Large Dogs
features: Dog Training Leash : Elevate your dog's recall skills with our dog waterproof leash. Ideal for outdoor activities like hiking, camping, and beach play, it fosters better obedience and a closer bond.

Weatherproof Durability : Crafted from PVC coated nylon webbing, our dog waterproof leash remains lightweight and strong even when wet. It's weatherproof, easy to clean, anti-odor and perfect for all conditions.
Strong and Soft leash : Experience a leash that's both strong and gentle. With a remarkable 600 lbs pull force resistance, it offers safety and comfort in various weather conditions.
Adventure Ready: Designed for active outdoor moments, our dog leash stands up to play, training, and exploration. It's a reliable companion for all your escapades.
Multi color and size: We provide different colors to choose from width 3/5 inch with length 5FT /10FT /15FT /30FT/ 50FT. Find the perfect fit for your dog's needs and your preferences.
